三戒：1．戒盲读。不加选择，一会儿看这类，一会儿看那类，徒耗时间，一无所得；2．戒浪读。虽经选择，而不确定目标，且忽作忽辍；3．戒死读。不反省，不详察，不求与事实相考证。（三）读书有四要：1．要与物的观察相印证；2．要与事的体验相融合；3．要配合目的、时间和需要；4．要思学合一。","totalCount":281,"users":[{"userVid":370912768,"name":"紫薇山居士","gender":1,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/Q3auHgzwzM6d77jXIgUiaHWj5lrYKdQRXtrhvpxxXB0LabB68NGgGsg/0"},{"userVid":19912705,"name":"ninja","gender":1,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/PiajxSqBRaEKM77ZPp49rUbWafulYib03PErAagyvuzbHsJaSOzmP1TQ/0"},{"userVid":77826051,"name":"一座城","nick":"一座城","gender":2,"avatar":"https://res.weread.qq.com/wravatar/WV0024-__xOwkry3H95YmY9u975285/0","isV":0,"vDesc":"青年麻醉医生"}]},{"bookId":"933559","userVid":305360024,"bookmarkId":"933559_18_4309-4498","chapterUid":18,"range":"4309-4498","markText":"（一）应该多看一些社会科学的书，懂得一些唯物史观、经济史观、人类学等常识。（二）应该多看一些论理学、心理学的书籍，懂得一些思想法则、心理现象。（三）应该多看一些自然科学的书，如生物学、物理学、天文学、地质学等，懂得一些天、地、人、物的历史和现状。","totalCount":262,"users":[{"userVid":54311936,"name":"葛志毅","gender":2,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/Q3auHgzwzM6Bdln5YRu884rFcdM37Qm831gRv2sBhficn4BQyPR445A/0"},{"userVid":347901443,"name":"欧阳伊雪","gender":2,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/rfgibhnp3kmjMssZGXibeGDWcOeZTnk7ItcQzdafGgo5BXaiaeIpqOnsoxH50GrpU9TicHOV7gcXHiaOXOEHibcJyjpA/132"},{"userVid":6100484,"name":"Jolene","nick":"Jolene","gender":2,"avatar":"https://res.weread.qq.com/wravatar/WV0019-k5fPVEISXgOfDg5Q~KG~va4/0","isV":0,"vDesc":"人文/文学/外语"}]},{"bookId":"933559","userVid":415609930,"bookmarkId":"933559_6_764-810","chapterUid":6,"range":"764-810","markText":"书籍是各种智识的宝库，读书为着要解决问题，否则可不必读。我们要用最经济的方法去读最有用的书。","totalCount":254,"users":[{"userVid":27109888,"name":"Fantasy","gender":1,"avatar":"https://wx.qlogo.cn/mmhead/ymiarLmfVUfib1HH1WpiaqMWySiaclp7ZtzTBXwic5tEpE0w/0"},{"userVid":29607424,"name":"D丶Knight","gender":1,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTJe2v5tzdicP1hIWhB9HJMyQvkMv2BqAXkNCPAfyKfnNsWHicfzX0T85CutW5a2WjOjEk72BOl3c2Rg/132"},{"userVid":4058283,"name":"Chauncy Wang","nick":"Chauncy Wang","gender":1,"avatar"